# Project Skills (Cursor)

This project uses shared skills. Since Cursor CLI has limited skill support,
use manual commands or switch to Cursor IDE for full MCP integration.

## Available Skills

### Deploy Skill
Deploy the application to target environment.

**Manual Command:**
```bash
./skills/shared/scripts/deploy-validate.sh <env>
./skills/shared/scripts/deploy-build.sh --env=<env>
./skills/shared/scripts/deploy-execute.sh --env=<env>
```

**Environments:** dev, staging, prod

---

### Test Skill
Run the test suite.

**Manual Command:**
```bash
./skills/shared/scripts/test-run.sh --type=all [--coverage]
```

**Types:** unit, integration, e2e, all

---

### Lint Skill
Run code linters.

**Manual Command:**
```bash
./skills/shared/scripts/lint-run.sh [--fix]
```

---

### Format Skill
Format code.

**Manual Command:**
```bash
./skills/shared/scripts/format-run.sh [--check]
```

---

## Usage Guidelines

When asked to perform a skill:
1. Inform the user that Cursor CLI has limited skill support
2. Provide the manual command to execute
3. Offer to help with the output

## For Full Skill Support

Recommend using Cursor IDE with MCP configuration for full skill integration.
MCP server: ./skills/shared/mcp-server/index.js
